    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The space station is infected by an unknown virus, turning all astronauts into bloodthirsty monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308950/extras/e47f9df194771c406634ca8601ff86e8.avif?t=1770260215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308950/extras_big/e47f9df194771c406634ca8601ff86e8.avif?t=1770260215 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're the only survivor, but your only means of escape, the Hover Bike, is broken. In a space inhabited solely by you and the monsters, your mission is to open doors using the console, find the crucial repair parts, fix the Hover Bike and escape！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308950/extras/92d8a9b8725652da454080256a6fd836.avif?t=1770260215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308950/extras_big/92d8a9b8725652da454080256a6fd836.avif?t=1770260215 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>This is no simple task!</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must maintain the oxygen supply and avoid monsters while searching for repair parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Exquisite space station scenes.</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore locations like the Ship Dock, Maintenance Room, and Control Room, but beware of deadly traps in the space station!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Puzzles in the space station.</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your wit to solve puzzles in the space station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308950/extras/43a69a59302682b3b27e1bb5a1be047d.avif?t=1770260215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308950/extras_big/43a69a59302682b3b27e1bb5a1be047d.avif?t=1770260215 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is created by <strong>@watase</strong> with YAHAHA Horror Game Kit and YAHAHA assists the creator with packaging and publishing the game based on their request. Yahaha Horror Gamekit is tailored for imaginative creators and players who adore horror games, all without the need for any programming expertise.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308950/extras/f0b9938cb45f4fb6f526c0858065e8d0.avif?t=1770260215\" width=720 height=216 /></span></p>",
